query.name: Predloge ki bi morale biti v effective stanju

queries.query: select object_name, mob_valid_from, r_version_label from mob_form_template where not mob_valid_from is nulldate and DATEDIFF(day, "mob_valid_from", date(today))<0 and not (any r_version_label = 'effective' or any r_version_label = 'archive')
select r_object_id from mob_subscriber_document where mob_subscriber_number (SPP stranke) ='<1>' and mob_type_id = 164 ENABLE (RETURN_RANGE 1 10 'r_modify_date desc')

queries.query: SELECT r_object_id FROM mob_incoming_invoice WHERE DATEDIFF(week, "r_modify_date" , DATE(TODAY))<=1 and r_creator_name='Captiva Administrator' ENABLE (RETURN_RANGE 1 100 'r_modify_date desc')
